Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So where do you guys wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we've got our own ship,\Nwe won't take the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just follow the log.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then it must be Water Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Water Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Above all, it's a city that made\Na name for itself with its shipyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Their technology is No. 1 in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna go there and get a\Nshipwright to join our crew for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This area should be okay, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy crap! The Going Merry\Nhas gotten this rickety?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A map?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll be helpful! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect. Once we get the money,\Nwe can go to the shipyard right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We can finally have\Nthe Going Merry repaired!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Go! Yagara!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your business! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash to the shipyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
