Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that such a convenient\Ncreature exists in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't rock much. It's comfortable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To the right! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,--The ball is headed your way!\N--Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Stop the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,--Pass the ball! Pass the ball!\N--This is neato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This area seems to be a residential area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This town really is built around canals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going? Sightseeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To the shipyard! We're gonna\Nhave our ship repaired!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go to the backstreet\Nshopping district first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Backstreet shopping district...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll turn right ahead of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my beautiful mademoiselle!\NHow about dinner with me tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about him. The guys\Naround here say that like it's a greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hurry up and go to work already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know. Stop nagging.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, people in this\Ntown are generous to outsiders--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or should I say they're overly friendly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You with the long nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--Nothing. I was just saying hey, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a fist in your face, pops?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, a hill is coming up. We're gonna\Ngo against the flow. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we go up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wrong way! Go right! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't matter even if the\Nwater is running downhill, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The canals even go above the rooftops!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're going the wrong way!\NWe have to go to the shopping district first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be so hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a rare opportunity.\NLet's stroll through the canals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hm?\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! L-Look! Look ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right! We're at the top of the hill!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fun but scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrrrgh! We went flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're falling. We're falling.\NWe're falling. We're falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're falling. We're falling. We're falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get full of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss! Our stuff is cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How about taking a look at our products?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got lots of superb\Nitems that are hard to find!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're now starting our 50%-off sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Things have gotten lively!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? We ended up in the shopping district!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you took a shortcut?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. You guys are actually smart, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been to such an\Nenergetic shopping district!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that! That's a huge bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Hey, it's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like he's about to eat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering its size, I wonder if this is a King.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Masks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they're pretty. They're gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's a party or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! These are freshly made\Nwater-water octopus dumplings!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Two water-water croquettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Both look yummy! Yagara, go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where're you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy! Where're you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask the Yagara!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome! What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you were hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Water-water meat is the Yagara's\Nfavorite food, although it's human food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Water-water? Then give me ten of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so good that the cooks from the gourmet\Ntown would secretly come to purchase them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It captivates your body and soul, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They... are... so... soft...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yummy!\N--What?! Is it that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy! Give me one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Buy it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nami! Pull the boat over to that shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,More masks... Now that I look closer,\Nthey seem to be everywhere in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people with masks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Some pirates started\Ncausing a ruckus at Dock #1!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better get there right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about it really carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's true that you guys repaired our ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but no matter how I looked at it,\NI thought the fee was too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're interrupting our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So... I decided not to pay--\Nnot even a single Berry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the perfect repairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, it was free!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Kalifa, what's going on over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Iceberg-san.\NThey're the customers for Dock #1.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the work has been completed,\Nthey're saying they won't pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... That is sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, it'd be wise not to tease craftsmen like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You son of a bitch!\NWatch carefully where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You bastards! Are you picking a fight?!\NWho do you think we are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you test fired the cannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not yet, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Who the hell are you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The pirate way of doing things doesn't\Nwork on craftsmen's turf, now, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... We're finally going to\Ngo to the shipbuilding island
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,by using a water gate elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A water gate elevator?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That tower-like thing is the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The elevator will go to the shipbuilding island,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,shipbuilding plant, and downtown Water Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hurry inside the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,One minute until the gate gets closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll happen inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! The water gate is now closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going up!\NWe're going up! We're going up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That happens. Then, this happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, they do this and that.\NSo that's why it's a water gate elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Water Seven is interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So they use water for all sorts of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you calling Mosshead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--Where's Robin-chan? She isn't on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, she isn't. She went\Nout with Chopper earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--She said she was going shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! Then are you\Nthe only one on the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What a boring environment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then. I'll go grocery shopping, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So make sure you watch the ship good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, he's already asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, fine. I'll leave the ship to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the world's No. 1 shipyard!\NDowntown Water Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, I see more ground around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are huge all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a huge town like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.71,0:16:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing that fountain up close\Nmakes it look especially big!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that crowd?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they watching the shipyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go see it! Go, Yagara!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look over there!\NIt's Lucci-san! He's so handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Paulie here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lulu's here! How refined he is!\NHe's truly a man's man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's manlier than Tilestone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hey, pops.\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It seems that some pirates\Ncaused a ruckus at this here Dock #1.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But, well, it ended when the\Ncraftsmen knocked them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no end to those fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:17:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shipwrights beat pirates up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you must be a voyager.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That crowd is... well, in short, busybodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Those shipwrights at the Galley-La\NCompany are admired by all the residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They're strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...and skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the pride of Water Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I'm looking forward to meeting them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up and go to\Nthe money-changing shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We can come back here later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It says that we're in the\Nbackstreet shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They call a place this lively the backstreet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So they have places that\Nwe can walk around, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The water is clear and the town is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Such beauty hasn't been\Nseen for the last 100 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is full of Sanjis...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a mask shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've noticed people are walking\Naround in town wearing those masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so they're wearing them, huh?\NI thought those were weird faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like they're holding a\Ncostume carnival every day right now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,on San Faldo, an island you\Ntake the sea train to get to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How come you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,People walking by are talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that you can hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a habit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Since my childhood, I've lived by trying to judge\Npeople's feelings and listening in on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--Doctor...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there! There's a bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we stop by here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,CP9...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin! I'm gonna go on ahead and go in, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm in my human form... it may be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a cool mask!\NWhat're you dressed up as?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... A human reindeer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're having fun, that's what's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we were attacking you in your sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you bastards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Identify yourselves!
