Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible! Usopp flew in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Hm? Hey, I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.50,0:23:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, that Usopp\Nhas a square-ish nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,--When it comes to guys,\Nnothing beats a round nose!\N--Well, welcome, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.97,0:23:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Iceberg, the boss of this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a big shot, pops?\NThen please repair our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,--Sure.\N--Whoa, that sounded frivolous!\NIs it okay to be that frivolous?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.18,0:23:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Franky Family and Iceberg-san"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.77,0:23:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
